{"tid":1548252,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪攰喇？","createTime":"2019-09-07T03:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T03:44:47.000Z","uid":70679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"10ea73237387b519e44fecaf97bd184c7260f60f","tid":1548252,"uid":70679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:20:11.000Z","msg":"我地搞左咁耐，會攰係正常，林鄭係依個時候話撤，一定會下意識想休息。<br />\n我明，大家都好攰，我都見到出黎既好似少左人，文宣既又細力左，某啲地方既連儂好似荒廢左咁&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n尋晚去樓下連儂牆睇，剛好見到個廢佬撕紙偷野，我當然即時衝出去影佢趕佢走。趕完我自己都灰左，因為以前係一定會有人係度，同我一齊趕，唔會得自己一個，但尋晚，我只有自己一個。<br />\n希望大家只係暫時攰休息下 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好留底我一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee2f2d4e285e09d7e98cd3871c8707fc4ae860f","tid":1548252,"uid":67074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAXvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=d95d5293\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n黎明來到要<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>光復</strong></span>這<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>香港</strong></span><br />\n同行兒女為正義<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>時代革命</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RBK1Uyp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRBK1Uyp.jpg&h=4972b138&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http